title: Ambrosia yogarestaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Western, Buffet, Take-out, Catering, European
description: Veggie buffet restaurant located 100 meters from Norrebro station, reachable by bus 66, 4A, 5A, 350S, and S-train F (yellow line). Features all-you-can-eat buffet for dinner. The dishes change depending on what vegetables are in-season, mainly organic. Offers a variety of drinks, including fresh pressed vegetable juice, ginger lemonade, and turmeric-milk made from rice milk and fresh turmeric. Honey is used in a few drinks (ask). On Saturday a yogic brunch is offered (no buffet). Cozy and colorful interior, established since 2008.
